{"title_page": "Bhagalpur College of Engineering", "text_new": "{{short description|One of the best Government engineering college in Bhagalpur, Bihar}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2017}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=July 2017}}\n{{Infobox university\n| name = Bhagalpur College of Engineering\n| native_name = \u092d\u093e\u0917\u0932\u092a\u0941\u0930 \u0905\u092d\u093f\u092f\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0923 \u092e\u0939\u093e\u0935\u093f\u0926\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0932\u092f\n| logo =\n| image = File:Bhagalpur_College_of_Engineering_logo.svg\n| caption =\n| established = 1960\n| type = [[State school|Public college]]\n| motto = \u092f\u094b\u0917\u0903 \u0915\u0930\u094d\u092e\u0938\u0941 \u0915\u094c\u0936\u0932\u092e\u094d (Sanskrit)\n| principal = Prof. Dr. Achintya Ranjan\n| chairman =\n| undergrad = 1000\n| postgrad =\n| staff = 72\n| faculty = 100\n| free_label = Acronym\n| free = BCE\n| students = 1200\n| city = [[Bhagalpur]]\n| state = [[Bihar]]\n| country = [[India]]\n| campus = Urban  {{convert|167|acre|km2}}\n| colors =\n| nickname = BCE Bhagalpur\n| affiliations = [[Aryabhatta Knowledge University]]\n| website = {{URL|http://www.bcebhagalpur.ac.in}}\n}}\n[[File:Main Academic Building.jpg|thumb|right|alt=A]]\n\n'''Bhagalpur College of Engineering''' ([[Devan\u0101gar\u012b]]: \u092d\u093e\u0917\u0932\u092a\u0941\u0930 \u0905\u092d\u093f\u092f\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0923 \u092e\u0939\u093e\u0935\u093f\u0926\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0932\u092f) (abbreviated as '''BCE''' '''Bhagalpur''') is a Government Technical Institution established in 1960 in [[Bhagalpur]], [[Bihar]], [[India]]. The institute offers full-time [[Bachelor of Technology]] (B.Tech)  degree programs. It is administered by the [[Department of Science and Technology, Bihar]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dst.bih.nic.in/EngineeringCollegeDetails.aspx|title=Department of Science & Technology :: List of Engineering College|website=dst.bih.nic.in|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.admissionjankari.com/college-details/be-b.tech/bhagalpur-college-of-engineering|title=Bhagalpur College Of Engineering {{!}} Bhagalpur {{!}} Bihar {{!}} BE/B.Tech - Admission Jankari|website=www.admissionjankari.com|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref> College is affiliated with [[Aryabhatta Knowledge University]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://akubihar.ac.in/Colleges/EngineeringDetails.aspx?SlNo=43|title=.:Official Website : Aryabhatta Knowledge University, Patna:.|website=akubihar.ac.in|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref>\n\n== History ==\nCollege was set up by the Department of Science and Technology, [[Government of Bihar]] in the year 1960. Earlier, the affiliation was under [[Tilka Manjhi Bhagalpur University|Tilkamanjhi Bhagalpur University]]. After the establishment of [[Aryabhatta Knowledge University]] in 2008, affiliation of the college is transferred to this university.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.edufever.com/bce-bhagalpur-college-of-engineering/|title=Bhagalpur College of Engineering, BCE Bhagalpur - Fees, Courses,Placement|last=Jha|first=Pragya|date=2016-11-29|website=Edufever|language=en-US|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref>\n== Admission ==\nEarlier, undergraduate admissions were done through the [[Bihar Combined Entrance Competitive Examination Board#BCECE|BCECE]] conducted by [[Bihar Combined Entrance Competitive Examination Board]]. From 2019 and onwards admissions is taken through [[BCECEB#UGEAC|UGEAC]] based on rank list of [[JEE Main]] conducted by [[National Testing Agency]].\n== Academic Departments ==\nBCE Bhagalpur have 9 Academic departments.\n* Department of [[Civil engineering|Civil Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Computer Science and Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Electrical engineering|Electrical Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Electronics and Communication engineering|Electronics and Communication Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Mechanical engineering|Mechanical Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Physics]]\n* Department of [[Chemistry]]\n* Department of [[Mathematics]]\n* Department of [[Humanities]]\n\n==Degree programs==\nCollege conducts educational programs leading to the degree of Bachelor of Technology (B. Tech.) in [[Civil engineering|Civil Engineering]], [[Computer Science and Engineering]],  [[Electrical engineering|Electrical Engineering]],  [[Electronics and Communication engineering|Electronics and Communication Engineering]], and [[Mechanical engineering|Mechanical Engineering]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.careers360.com/colleges/bhagalpur-college-of-engineering-bhagalpur|title=Bhagalpur College of Engineering, Bhagalpur|last=https://www.careers360.com|website=www.careers360.com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref>\n== Facilities ==\n* High Tech Labs\n* Indoor Stadium\n* Computer Science Arena\n* College Library\n* Commercial Bank(UCO bank)\n* High Speed Wifi\n* Canteen\n* Co-operative store\n* Post office\n* Student Amenity Center\n* Boy's and Girl's Hostels\n* Guest House\n* UCO bank  ATM\n* Playground\n\n== College festivals ==\nBhagalpur College of Engineering organizes '''Technoriti''' as its annual festival every year from 2012. Started with the name '''AAGHAZ''' the festival comprises Parakram the annual Sports meet, Umang the Cultural festival and technical fest. Later in 2013, the name aaghaz was changed to Technoriti by the student organization which additionally included Sangam as the Alumni meet of BCE Bhagalpur.\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.bcebhagalpur.ac.in/ Official website]\n* [https://bceceboard.bihar.gov.in/ BCECE Board website]\n* [http://akubihar.ac.in/ AKU website]\n* [http://dst.bih.nic.in/ DST, Bihar website]\n\n{{Aryabhatta Knowledge University}}\n{{Engineering Colleges in Bihar}}\n{{Portal|Education|Engineering|India}}\n\n[[Category:Engineering colleges in Bihar]]\n[[Category:Education in Bhagalpur district]]\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Bhagalpur]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1960]]\n[[