-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.admissionjankari.com/college-details/be-b.tech/bhagalpur-college-of-engineering|title=Bhagalpur College Of Engineering {{!}} Bhagalpur {{!}} Bihar {{!}} BE/B.Tech - Admission Jankari|website=www.admissionjankari.com|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref> College is affiliated with [[Aryabhatta Knowledge University]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://akubihar.ac.in/Colleges/EngineeringDetails.aspx?SlNo=43|title=.:Official Website : Aryabhatta Knowledge University, Patna:.|website=akubihar.ac.in|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref>\n== History ==\nCollege was set up by the Department of Science and Technology, [[Government of Bihar]] in the year 1960. Earlier, the affiliation was under [[Tilka Manjhi Bhagalpur University|Tilkamanjhi Bhagalpur University]]. After the establishment of [[Aryabhatta Knowledge University]] in 2008, affiliation of the college is transferred to this university.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.edufever.com/bce-bhagalpur-college-of-engineering/|title=Bhagalpur College of Engineering, BCE Bhagalpur - Fees, Courses,Placement|last=Jha|first=Pragya|date=2016-11-29|website=Edufever|language=en-US|access-date=2020-02-01}}</ref>\n== Admission ==\nEarlier, undergraduate admissions were done through the [[Bihar Combined Entrance Competitive Examination Board#BCECE|BCECE]] conducted by [[Bihar Combined Entrance Competitive Examination Board]]. From 2019 and onwards admissions is taken through [[BCECEB#UGEAC|UGEAC]] based on rank list of [[JEE Main]] conducted by [[National Testing Agency]].\n== Academic Departments ==\nBCE Bhagalpur have 9 Academic departments.\n* Department of [[Civil engineering|Civil Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Computer Science and Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Electrical engineering|Electrical Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Electronics and Communication engineering|Electronics and Communication Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Mechanical engineering|Mechanical Engineering]]\n* Department of [[Physics]]\